---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Top Gear Decide"
  description="How Top Gear Decide (topgeardecide.com) collects, uses and protects your information, including cookies, affiliate links and your privacy choices."
  path="/privacy-policy"
>
  <main class="page">
    <div class="container page-wrap">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="lead">Last updated: 2025</p>

      <p>Your privacy matters to us. This policy describes what information Top Gear Decide (topgeardecide.com) collects, how we use it, and the choices you have. By using our website, you agree to the practices described below.</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect two broad types of information. The first is information you choose to give us — for example, your name and email address when you fill out our contact form. The second is information collected automatically as you browse, such as your IP address, browser type, device, referring page and the pages you view. This automatic data helps us understand how the site is used and how to improve it.</p>

      <h2>Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <p>Like most websites, we use cookies and similar technologies. Cookies are small files stored on your device that help the site function, remember preferences and measure traffic. Our affiliate partners and analytics providers may also set cookies to attribute referrals and understand audience behavior. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, though some parts of the site may not work as intended.</p>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To respond to your messages and requests.</li>
        <li>To operate, maintain and improve the website and its content.</li>
        <li>To measure the performance of our pages and affiliate links.</li>
        <li>To detect, prevent and address technical issues or misuse.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Affiliate Links and Third Parties</h2>
      <p>Our pages contain affiliate links, including links through the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program. When you click these links, the destination retailer may collect information according to its own privacy policy. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of any third-party sites you visit. See our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for more detail on how these links work.</p>

      <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share limited data with service providers who help us run the site — such as analytics and hosting providers — and only to the extent needed to perform those services. We may also disclose information if required by law.</p>

      <h2>Your Choices</h2>
      <p>You can opt out of non-essential cookies through your browser, and you can ask us to delete any personal information you have submitted through our contact form. To make a request, contact us using the details on our <a href="/contact">Contact</a> page.</p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>This website is not directed to children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from them.</p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time. When we do, we will revise the "last updated" date at the top of this page. Continued use of the site after changes means you accept the revised policy.</p>

      <h2>Contact Us by Email</h2>
      <p>You can also reach us directly by email:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>General questions &amp; feedback: <a href="mailto:info@topgeardecide.com">info@topgeardecide.com</a></li>
        <li>Advertising &amp; affiliate partnerships: <a href="mailto:affiliate@topgeardecide.com">affiliate@topgeardecide.com</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
